Instead of
;; Recompile if .elc exists.
                (add-hook (make-local-variable 'after-save-hook)
                          (lambda ()
                            (byte-force-recompile default-directory)))
why not only do what's necessary?
;; Recompile if .elc exists.
                (add-hook (make-local-variable 'after-save-hook)
                          (lambda ()
                            (byte-compile-file buffer-file-name)))

